### Configuration Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### 1. CREATE - Register a new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/users

{
    "display_name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane.doe@example.com",
}

###

### 2. READ - Get all users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

###

### 3. READ - Get a specific user by ID
# @name getUser
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/123

###

### 4. UPDATE - Update user details (Full Update)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/123

{
    "display_name": "Jane Smith",
    "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
}

###

### 5. UPDATE - Partially update user (e.g., change role)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/123

{
    "role": "super-user"
}

###

### 6. DELETE - Remove a user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/123
